OL,8,G1930FEastEnders
OL,9,     GIt's election day, and Ian and
OL,10,     GElaine are anxiously awaiting the
OL,11,     Gresults. Nicola tries to support
OL,12,     GGeorge, and Max's jealousy mounts.
