OL,14,     GWith the leaderboard closer than
OL,15,     Gever, all four teams leave Zaamin
OL,16,     GNational Park and race towards
OL,17,     Gthe next checkpoint, Almaty,
OL,18,     GKazakhstan's former Soviet-era
OL,19,     Gcapital.
